<div class="menues-mod">
	<h2>메뉴관리</h2>
	<p><i>Pick a menu from the list or Add a menu from input</i></p>
	<div class="row menu-panel">
		<div class="col-md-12">	
			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-heading">
					<span class="panel-title">메뉴 정보 수정</span>
				</div>
				<div class="panel-body">
					<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>
					<p>메뉴 정보를 입력해주세요.</p>
					<form>
						<div class="form-group">
							<label for="nameInput">이름</label>
							<input type="text" class="form-control" name="name" id="nameInput" placeholder="이름">
						</div>
						<div class="form-group">
							<label for="linkInput">URL 또는 라우트 주소</label>
							<input type="text" class="form-control" name="url" placeholder="링크 주소">
						</div>
						<span class="btn-group btn-group-justified" role="group">
							<a class="btn btn-default" role="button">확인</a>
							<a class="btn btn-default" role="button">취소</a>
						</span>
					</form>					
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>